theme_override_font_sizes/normal_font_size = 18
bbcode_enabled = true
text = "[center]
[b]Goal:[/b]
You need to get to a shaman. In order to do so you need to pickup resources along the way and protect them from thieves while camping.

[b]Controls:[/b]
- [b]Select Parrot:[/b] Click with LMB
- [b]Move Parrot:[/b] Click on ground with RMB
- [b]Deselect:[/b] Click on empty space with LMB

[i]The stretcher moves automatically. Keep your gatherers close or they will be lost in the forest![/i]
[/center]"

